---
title: Pork Chops & Apple Rosemary Pan Sauce with Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: These, friends, are not your average pork chops. In fact, our chefs gave ’em a restaurant-worthy makeover, transforming the everyday protein into something above and beyond. The chops are seared to perfection, then drizzled with an ultra-savory, rosemary-flecked apple pan sauce. The sides? Just as impressive. We’re serving up creamy mashed potatoes and roasted Brussels sprouts to round everything out. Get ready for maximum dinnertime deliciousness.
